item.title: How do i make client for others to downlaod
item.dc:creator: @hasumon hasumon
item.description:
@hasumon wrote:

brad simpson298:

can u do it on TV or talk to me on skype plzz??

I am sure that you are perfectly capable of doing this yourself. Just compress the folder with winrar or winzip as a .zip or .rar file and upload it to any uploading external site. After uploading it, the website should offer a URL to the download for others to use (i.e. the people you want to use to connect to your server).

brad simpson298:

how do i get people on my server with a client what do i put i megafire.

You just need to upload the client (and client cache if they are seperated). The others only need the client to connect to your server (if you set the I.P. in the client correctly and portforwarded correctly).
